    "Alcove installs use standard wall-fed plumbing — the cheapest, simplest route. Freestanding tubs need either a floor-mounted filler (elegant, pricier, must be positioned before the slab or floor is closed) or wall taps reaching over the rim. Waste position matters too: it must line up with existing floor penetrations or the floor gets opened. None of this is difficult; all of it is cheaper decided early.":"壁龛安装用标准墙面出水——最便宜最简单。独立缸则需要落地龙头（优雅、较贵、必须在封地坪前定位）或探过缸缘的墙面龙头。排水位置也要对上现有的楼板开孔，否则就得开地板。这些都不难；但都越早决定越省钱。",
    "3 · Cleaning and living with it":"3 · 清洁与日常相处",
    "Freestanding means more visible floor to mop and a back edge to reach if placed near a wall. Built-ins hide their sides but grow silicone joints where rim meets tile — the part that eventually discolours and needs redoing. Call it a draw, with different chores.":"独立式意味着更多要拖的地板，靠墙摆的话还有一道背缝要够。嵌入式藏起了侧面，却在缸缘与瓷砖交界长出硅胶缝——那条最终会变色、需要重打的缝。算平手，只是家务不同。",
    "4 · Cost":"4 · 成本",
    "Comparable quality costs comparable money at the tub level. The difference is installation: alcove is cheapest; drop-in adds the deck build; freestanding adds floor plumbing and, for heavy materials, possibly a floor-loading check. A light acrylic freestanding tub (27–45 kg) largely removes the structural question — one reason it's the default choice upstairs.":"同等品质的缸体价格相当，差别在安装：壁龛最便宜；嵌入台面式要加做台座；独立式要加地面水电，重的材质还可能要做楼板承重确认。轻巧的亚克力独立缸（27–45 kg）基本消除了结构问题——这是它成为楼上首选的原因之一。",
    "5 · Style and resale":"5 · 风格与转售",
    "A freestanding tub is the centrepiece move — sculptural, photogenic, and the first thing an inspection notices. Built-ins disappear into the architecture, which is exactly right for compact family bathrooms and wet-room layouts. Neither is universally \"more premium\"; execution decides.":"独立缸是空间的主角之举——雕塑感、上镜，看房时第一眼就被注意到。嵌入式则隐入建筑本身，对紧凑的家庭浴室和湿区布局来说恰恰正确。没有谁「天生更高级」；成败在执行。",
    "The verdict":"结论",
    "for compact rooms, shower-over-bath layouts, and budget-led renovations. Choose":"适合紧凑空间、淋浴叠浴缸的布局与预算优先的翻新。选择",
    "freestanding":"独立式",
    "when the room has space to give and you want the bath to be the room's statement. And if your space sits awkwardly between standard sizes either way — that's what":"则适合房间有余裕、想让浴缸成为空间宣言的时候。而如果你的空间不上不下、卡在标准尺寸之间——那正是",
    "custom dimensions":"定制尺寸",
    "a made-to-order shape":"与量身定做的造型",
    "are for. We build both freestanding and drop-in forms, in":"的用武之地。独立式与嵌入台面式我们都做，材质可选",
    "acrylic and solid surface":"亚克力与人造石",
    "Do freestanding bathtubs take up more space?":"独立浴缸更占空间吗？",
    "They need breathing room — at least 100–150 mm of clearance around the tub, ideally 300 mm on the access side — so the same tub occupies more floor area than an alcove install. In generous rooms this is a feature; in tight rooms it's the deciding constraint.":"它需要呼吸空间——缸周至少 100–150 mm 间隙，靠近侧最好 300 mm——所以同一个缸占的楼面比壁龛安装大。房间宽裕时这是优点；房间紧张时它就是决定性限制。",
    "Are freestanding tubs harder to clean?":"独立缸更难清洁吗？",
    "The tub itself is no harder, but you gain floor to mop and (if placed near a wall) a gap to reach. Choosing full wall clearance or a wall-snug back-to-wall design avoids the awkward middle ground.":"缸本身不难，但多了要拖的地板，靠墙摆还有一道缝要够。要么留足与墙的间隙，要么选贴墙式（back-to-wall）设计，避开尴尬的中间地带。",
    "Is a freestanding bathtub more expensive to install?":"独立浴缸安装更贵吗？",
    "Usually somewhat — floor-mounted or exposed plumbing costs more than a standard wall-fed alcove connection, and a heavy tub may need a floor-loading check. The tub itself spans the same price range as quality built-ins.":"通常略贵——落地或明装水电比标准壁龛墙面接驳贵，重的缸可能还要做楼板承重确认。缸体本身与优质嵌入式处于同一价格带。",
    "Can I put a freestanding tub in a small bathroom?":"小浴室能放独立缸吗？",
    "Yes — choose a compact deep soaker (1400–1500 mm) and give it honest clearance rather than forcing a large tub against the walls. A small freestanding tub with room around it looks bigger than a big tub jammed in.":"能——选紧凑深泡缸（1400–1500 mm）并诚实地留出间隙，而不是把大缸硬顶到墙上。四周有余裕的小独立缸，看起来反而比塞满的大缸更大气。",
    "Whichever you choose — make it yours.":"无论选哪种——都做成你的。",
    "Freestanding or drop-in, we shape it to your room and your bather. Sketch it in five minutes and get a photoreal render in 48 hours.":"独立式或嵌入式，我们都照你的房间和入浴者来塑形。花五分钟画出来，48 小时收到拟真渲染图。",
