    "The trade programme":"专业方案","Built for the way designers actually work.":"为设计师真实的工作方式而设。",
    "Bring the curve you've been told is \"not possible\" — that's our starting point.":"把那条被说「做不出来」的曲线带来——那正是我们的起点。",
    "Trade pricing — 15–25% off retail, factory-direct":"专业价——零售价 75–85 折，工厂直供",
    "We build directly from your CAD — any curve, any dimension":"直接依你的 CAD 制造——任意曲线、任意尺寸",
    "Sample priority + a dedicated account contact, not a queue":"样品优先＋专属对接窗口，不用排队",
    "White-glove 3D rounds you can present straight to your client":"白手套级 3D 修改回合，可直接向客户提案",
    "Specialty finishes: gold leaf, matte, stone-look, custom colour-match":"特殊饰面：金箔、哑光、仿石、定制配色",
    "$500 credit when you share the finished installation photos":"分享完工安装照片即获 $500 抵扣金",
    "How we fit your studio":"我们如何配合你的工作室","Three ways designers use us.":"设计师使用我们的三种方式。",
    "CAD-to-production":"CAD 直达生产",
    "Send your Rhino, SketchUp or DWG file. We manufacture to it directly — in acrylic or solid surface — an advantage catalogue brands can’t offer.":"发来你的 Rhino、SketchUp 或 DWG 文件。我们直接照此制造——亚克力或人造石皆可——这是型录品牌给不了的优势。",
    "White-label storefront":"白标店面",
    "Showcase your own designs; we manufacture only when your client orders. You keep the relationship and the margin.":"展示你自己的设计；客户下单我们才生产。客户关系与利润都归你。",
