    "Custom acrylic starts from AUD $2,990, and most projects land between $3,500 and $8,000. Solid surface starts from about $4,500. The design studio shows a live estimate as you size your tub — before you talk to anyone.":"定制亚克力 AUD $2,990 起，多数项目落在 $3,500–$8,000；人造石约 $4,500 起。在设计工作室调整尺寸时就能看到即时估价——完全不必先跟任何人谈。",
