    "48 hours to your photoreal 3D render, 4–6 weeks in production, then 2–4 weeks freight — about 8–10 weeks door to door, with progress photos along the way.":"48 小时出拟真 3D 渲染图，生产 4–6 周，运输 2–4 周——从下单到进家门约 8–10 周，途中持续附进度照片。",
    "Is the $399 design fee refundable?":"$399 设计费可以退吗？",
    "It is fully credited to your order, and 2–3 refinement rounds are included. If you decide not to proceed, the render and spec sheet are yours to keep.":"它可全额折抵订单，并包含 2–3 轮修改。若你决定不继续，渲染图与规格书都归你所有。",
    "What about delivery and installation?":"配送与安装怎么处理？",
    "We deliver crated and insured across Australia. Acrylic tubs are a comfortable two-person lift and sit on standard floors without reinforcement — any licensed plumber can complete the install.":"全澳洲木箱投保配送。亚克力浴缸两人即可轻松搬抬、放在标准楼板上不需补强——任何持牌水电工都能完成安装。",
    "What warranty do I get?":"保修是什么？",
    "A 10-year structural warranty on acrylic and 15-year on solid surface, backed by Australian-based after-sales service.":"亚克力 10 年结构保修，人造石 15 年，并由澳洲在地售后团队支持。",
    "Can I return a custom tub?":"定制浴缸可以退货吗？",
    "Because every tub is built to a spec you sign off before production, wrong-size returns don't happen. If anything arrives damaged or out of spec, we repair or remake it under warranty.":"因为每个浴缸都依你签署确认的规格制造，所以不会发生尺寸错误的退货。若到货有损坏或与规格不符，我们会在保修内修复或重做。",
    "What partners say.":"合作伙伴怎么说。",
    "Here's exactly what happens — and what it costs — from first sketch to a finished tub installed in your bathroom.":"从第一张草图到浴缸装进你家浴室，每一步会发生什么、要花多少钱，这里说得清清楚楚。",
    "No fine print surprises":"没有小字陷阱",
