    "Typical price":"典型价格",
    "Custom acrylic from AUD $2,990 — most projects land between $3,500 and $8,000. Solid surface from about $4,500. Your design studio estimate updates live as you size it.":"定制亚克力 AUD $2,990 起——多数项目落在 $3,500–$8,000；人造石约 $4,500 起。设计工作室的估价会随尺寸即时更新。",
    "The $399 design fee":"$399 设计费",
    "Includes the photoreal render, the signed spec sheet and 2–3 refinement rounds — and it's fully credited to your order. Don't proceed? The files are yours to keep.":"包含拟真渲染图、签署的规格书与 2–3 轮修改——且可全额折抵订单。不继续？文件归你所有。",
    "Payment & financing":"付款与分期",
    "Payment milestones are confirmed on your quote before production begins. Afterpay and Zip financing from around AUD $130/month on a $4,000 tub.":"付款节点在生产前于报价单上确认。Afterpay 与 Zip 分期，$4,000 的浴缸约每月 AUD $130 起。",
