    "Returns on a custom piece":"定制品的退货",
    "You sign off the spec before the mould opens, so wrong-size returns don't happen. Anything damaged or out of spec is repaired or remade under warranty.":"开模前你先签署确认规格，所以不会有尺寸错误的退货。任何损坏或与规格不符，都在保修内修复或重做。",
